}} Table  AlignDefault ColWidthDefault AlignDefault 
 Dr. Qure AlignDefault 
  Color|orange|[Dr. Qure]}} 
 Hmm... Now where did I put that...? 
  Color|purple|[Hello?]}} 
  Color|gray|He's deep in thought while trying to find something in his office.}} 
  Color|orange|[Dr. Qure]}} 
 Oh! I'm terribly sorry, I didn't notice you come in. What can I do for you? 
  Color|purple|[I was wondering more what I could do for you.]}} 
  Color|purple|[How about some medical jokes?]}} 
  Color|orange|[Dr. Qure]}} 
 Oh, really now? Well I suppose there is this one thing... 
  Color|orange|[Dr. Qure]}} 
 You see, I've lost the ingredients to make a special vitality remedy commonly used in these parts, quite a marvelous elixir! If you could fetch me some of those I could apply it to you for your travels too!  
  Color|purple|[I'll pass for now. They might still be in your office anyway!]}}  
  Color|orange|[Dr. Qure]}} 
 You know what? You could be right! 
  Color|gray|He goes back to searching through his desk... 
  Color|purple|[I'm in. Where should I start?]}} 
  Color|orange|[Dr. Qure]}} 
 Well, first of all, I require a Tenebre Mushroom from some fungal caves in the nearby islands.  
&o  1/2 - Travel to   Link   Fungus Thorn Cave Fungus_Thorn_Cave wikilink in order to obtain a Tenebre Mushroom 
&o  2/2 - Once you have a Tenebre Mushroom return to Dr. Qure Table  AlignDefault ColWidthDefault AlignDefault 
 Dr. Qure AlignDefault 
  Color|orange|[Dr. Qure]}} 
 Ah perfect! You found one!  
  Color|gray|The Doctor chucks some of the mushroom into a mortar and begins to grind it into a fine paste.}} 
  Color|purple|[Alright then, what's next?]}} 
  Color|orange|[Dr. Qure]}} 
 Hmm, a fresh Saragundi Sapling from a nearby forest. I'd say the Feyrune Forest would have an ample supply.  
&o  1/2 - Travel to   Link   Feyrune Forest Feyrune_Forest wikilink and retrieve a Saragundi Sapling 
&o  2/2 - Once you have a Saragundi Sapling, return to Dr. Qure Table  AlignDefault ColWidthDefault AlignDefault 
 Dr. Qure AlignDefault 
  Color|orange|[Dr. Qure]}} 
 Fantastic, it looks to be in perfect health! 
  Color|gray|The Doctor throws some leaves of the sapling into the mortar.}} 
  Color|purple|[What's the final ingredient?]}} 
  Color|orange|[Dr. Qure]}} 
 So, finally, I require a bottle of Kelp Oil. Unfortunately, some pirates had stolen the last bottle I had from me... I believe they've gone back to their base camp in the Spiral Island. 
  Color|purple|[Lovely...]}} 
  Color|orange|[Dr. Qure]}} 
 Yes, well I suppose it shouldn't be too much harder than fetching the other supplies.  
&o  1/2 - Travel to   Link   Spiral Island Spiral_Island wikilink to retrieve some Kelp Oil 
&o  2/2 - Once you have some Kelp Oil, return to Dr. Qure Table  AlignDefault ColWidthDefault AlignDefault 
 Dr. Qure AlignDefault 
  Color|orange|[Dr. Qure]}} 
 Great work! That's the final ingredient! 
  Color|gray|He pours a drop of the oil into the mortar, and then puts the mixture into a vial.}} 
  Color|purple|[So, does the medicine work?]}} 
  Color|orange|[Dr. Qure]}} 
 Of course it does! Applying it should give the person great vitality for a good while! With this fresh supply, I should have enough for weeks! Take this for your troubles.   AlignDefault 
 VITAL NEEDS COMPLETE! 
 Awarded 28 Crystalline Shards and access to Dr. Qure's healing remedy!  
